    <item>
      <title>葛兰素史克药物在高级研究中有助于预防严重哮喘发作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/gsk-drug-helps-prevent-severe-asthma-attacks-in-advanced-studies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葛兰素史克公司（GSK Plc）的实验药物在两项后期研究中有助于预防严重的哮喘发作，这为该药物的开发铺平了道路，该英国公司表示，该药物的年销售额可能达到 30 亿英镑（39 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/gsk-drug-helps-prevent-severe-asthma-attacks-in-advanced-studies</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
