      <title>对 Apple iPhone 16 发布会的期待</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-09/can-apple-make-a-software-launch-sexy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果预计将发布新的 iPhone 16 系列手机，并对 Apple Watch 和 AirPods 耳机进行重大改进。这对可穿戴设备业务来说是一个重要时刻。Ed Ludlow 今早在库比蒂诺的 Apple Park 预告了“彭博监控”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-09/can-apple-make-a-software-launch-sexy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 13:27:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
